spell.wizardry_tales:locating.desc=Tries to get your location in the world through mana pulsations.

spell.wizardry_tales:water_arrow=Water Arrow
spell.wizardry_tales:water_arrow.desc=Creates Magical Water and condenses it to create a Water Arrow.

spell.wizardry_tales:advanced_water_arrow=Greater Water Arrow
spell.wizardry_tales:advanced_water_arrow.desc=Water Arrows will inflict more damage against Undead creatures, such as Zombies or Skeletons.

spell.wizardry_tales:earth_bending=Earth Bending
spell.wizardry_tales:earth_bending.desc=Harness the elemental power of earth from Grass or Dirt to conjure a new block.

spell.wizardry_tales:focused_teleportation=Focused Teleportation
spell.wizardry_tales:focused_teleportation.desc=Take a teleportation scroll in offhand and cast this spell with main hand to teleport to your bound location!

spell.wizardry_tales:entangle=Entangle
spell.wizardry_tales:entangle.desc=Entangles the target, increasing fire damage while active and slowing down their movements.

spell.wizardry_tales:summon_ember=Summon Ember
spell.wizardry_tales:summon_ember.desc=Summons an Ember that flies and ignites enemies.

spell.wizardry_tales:leaf_disguise=Leaf Disguise
spell.wizardry_tales:leaf_disguise.desc=Covers the caster with leaves and if caster is sneaking, enters disguise state. Melee attack while disguised to deal extra damage!

spell.wizardry_tales:burning_disease=Burning Disease
spell.wizardry_tales:burning_disease.desc=Fills the target's body with fire. Burning internal wounds made by this magic effect will damage the target even more over time.

spell.wizardry_tales:blooming=Blooming
spell.wizardry_tales:blooming.desc=Conjures a flower on the ground that poisons those who step on it.

spell.wizardry_tales:binding=Arcane Binding
spell.wizardry_tales:binding.desc=Binds the item to the caster, so only they can use it.

spell.wizardry_tales:chanting=Chanting
spell.wizardry_tales:chanting.desc=Inscribe spell in this slot, and `add condition on spell`. This will allow you to cast said hand-made spell.

spell.wizardry_tales:conjure_ice_halberd=Conjure Ice Halberd
spell.wizardry_tales:conjure_ice_halberd.desc=Conjures an Ice Halberd, attacks can stack Frostbite duration.

spell.wizardry_tales:storm_armour=Storm Armour
spell.wizardry_tales:storm_armour.desc=From the thunderous echoes of the distant past, a set of Lightning Armour is conjured. It was once worn by a famous hero and leader of his people.

spell.wizardry_tales:mantis_agility=Mantis Agility
spell.wizardry_tales:mantis_agility.desc=Imbues your limbs with the deadly agility of a mantis. Increases movement speed and how fast you can swing your arms.

spell.wizardry_tales:teleportation_curse=Teleportation Curse
spell.wizardry_tales:teleportation_curse.desc=Causes target to be teleported randomly every 10 seconds.

